rows.text: While Anushka is in search of a boy who has proof about her sister's kidnappers, She crosses path with Chakor. Both head out to a party organised by Imli in Azadganj, hoping to find the boy there. Balwant is also present at the party.

Teni and Anushka's Life got connected to each other in unknowing way as Teni helped Anushka getting proof against Rantej and tried to help Anushka in getting justice for her younger sister Jhanvi. But Anushka loses the proof saving Teni's Life from Rantej. Rantej turns up enemy against Teni and Parth and decides to teach a lesson to Teni for helping Anushka. Parth is beaten up by Rantej and his goons and is hanged to death. Anushka and Teni rush to save Parth. Teni endangered her life to save Parth and manages to escape.
Chakor arrives Veerpur to Help Anushka in finding her missing paternal grandmother, Ammaji.
Udaan, Tu Aashiqui, Ishq Mein Marjawan, Shakti - Astitva Ke Ehsaas Ki, Savitri Devi College & Hospital, Dil Se Dil Tak and Belan Wali Bahu

To foil Harman and Jasleen's Marriage, Preeto invites Anushka, Saanchi, Veer, Chakor, Suraj, Aditya, Teni, Parth and Pankti to help her in her pursuit. Roopa and Shorvori also arrives to give a dance performance at Soumya's House. Anushka arrives at Soumya's House, to stop the marriage of Harman and Jasleen. She tries to convince Soumya to stop the marriage of her own husband to another lady as they both love each other.
